
ERROR: The -pa parameter has been deprecated.  Please use the newer
      "-threads #" parameter which precisely controls the maximum
       number of simultaneous threads this program will use. Note that
       the -pa parameter previously controlled the number of simultaneous
       batches each run with rmblast using 4 threads, therefore -pa 4 could
       potentially have used up to 16 threads.  Keep this in mind when
       comparing runtime differences between versions.

